				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/Ch%C3%A2n-l%E1%BA%A1c/poem-4i1FVGwGY73j7nqWTCvi0g">Chân lạc - 真樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/D%E1%BB%AF-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ng%C3%B4-%C4%91%C3%A0i-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-OvOoUoSjrKpHjFQISmC1uw">Dữ Dương Đình Ngô đài biệt - 與陽亭吳台別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Xu-Ng%C3%B4n-th%E1%BA%A3o-c%C3%A1c-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1xg3hi80FKcKoSCSEece2g">Hí đề Xu Ngôn thảo các tam thập nhị vận - 戲題樞言草閣三十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/H%E1%BB%89-t%C3%ACnh-thi/poem-VxiX2S8FM201wNOj-Wt0GA">Hỉ tình thi - 喜晴詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/author-7dFsTrXHz60sugbdOHPrjQ">Mạc Đĩnh Chi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tri%E1%BB%87t/H%E1%BB%93-T%E1%BB%AD-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-EDMdnTxcfZzefWT10PuiYA">Hồ Tử ca kỳ 1 - 瓠子歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tri%E1%BB%87t/author-gLGd-Bchdqe6FBWqpEd9Qw">Lưu Triệt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/H%E1%BB%A3i-ni%C3%AAn-t%C3%A0n-thu-ng%E1%BA%ABu-t%C3%A1c/poem-jGKoELqZrB-rKaeNSZ6HAw">Hợi niên tàn thu ngẫu tác - 亥年殘秋偶作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nam-tr%C3%AC/poem-1SAz4IPXlcjehpcf2UezrA">Nam trì - 南池</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Th%C3%B4n-c%C6%B0-c%E1%BA%A3m-s%E1%BB%B1-k%C3%BD-tr%C3%ACnh-B%C4%83ng-H%E1%BB%93-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-c%C3%B4ng/poem-p7gF0UyscYXFraj2_CM0YA">Thôn cư cảm sự ký trình Băng Hồ tướng công - 村居感事寄呈冰壼相公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/V%C4%83n-c%C3%B9ng-d%C3%A2n-m%E1%BA%ABu-t%E1%BB%AD-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BB%B1c-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-LdgFCHWV9LXwEs_t-X4Thg">Văn cùng dân mẫu tử tương thực hữu cảm - 聞窮民母子相食有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-7-H%E1%BA%AFc-b%E1%BA%A1ch-th%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-YZOrUP7uTarUbVMoxe5ajw">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 7 - Hắc bạch thạch - 詠富祿八景其七－黑白石</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
